yads.doi.lib
Class DObject

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--yads.doi.lib.DObject
public class DObject
extends java.lang.Object

A DObject manages the resource hierarchy associated with a DOI public identifier. This class defines methods for manipulating and persisting DObjects. DObjects are serialized across client/service transactions as RDF/XML instances (see DObjectInstance)..

Version:
0.1
Author:
Tony Hammond
